{"tid":1134912,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金希澈真係巧巧人 希望大家唔好再反她..","createTime":"2019-05-02T03:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T04:27:46.000Z","uid":46435,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8386b4ef91e8cfffebe099d8980e02462135cd2f","tid":1134912,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:44:54.000Z","msg":"久違的把&lt;偶像學校&gt;時學生的面談申請書拿出來看<br />\n<br />\n即使是現在我也常常搜尋學生們的名字，然後吟誦. 我有一點點人臉識別障礙，所以常常想不起臉長怎樣的關係..😥😢<br />\n<br />\n但是跟學生偶遇時<br />\n&quot;老師 好久不見愛! 你記得我是誰嗎?&quot;<br />\n這樣問我的話，因為我記憶力有限萬一.. 真的萬一我不想不起來的話，那個學生會感到受傷，就自己測試記憶力🤔🙄<br />\n<br />\n我的學生們<br />\n雖然大家都能實現自己的歌手夢就好了, 即使不是歌手，也希望不管何時能和好的人見面，一起製造美好的回憶，健健康康的!<br />\n因為我所看到的你們，真的是最棒最好的學生呀🤗🏫❤&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4RCD63R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4RCD63R.jpg&h=ca2c08f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zMAaYax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzMAaYax.jpg&h=dc772cf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GmDTbvB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmDTbvB.jpg&h=fe04da62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希澈老師😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭"},{"pid":"1cc197bd0c204ede8b2e43b233ae9c48266cc3fa","tid":1134912,"uid":1408,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:48:47.000Z","msg":"幾時有人反過希澈"},{"pid":"6bbdaa87bf45d4bbff828adc9ff5aacb774fede6","tid":1134912,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:49:43.000Z","msg":"傻閪來"},{"pid":"8afe78e950b3881340ced68f14ea58ba11f5cc26","tid":1134912,"uid":52073,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:50:02.000Z","msg":"死傻鳩希澈收聲啦"},{"pid":"1eee05b175b5c2da02b0cfc4619649ffcc6c01f4","tid":1134912,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:52:50.000Z","msg":"做咩學友同牙喪成日屌金希澈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg